## Quality Gate

Before declaring a task complete run

```
make check
```

The Makefile will run

```
ruff check .
ruff format --check .
mypy .
poetry run pytest -m smoke
```

Report results after running.

Full suite (`smoke + contract + integration + fuzz`) runs in CI nightly,
not per-commit.

