## Security

Never commit secrets.

```
.env.qa, .env.stg, .env.prod  → gitignored
.env.example                  → committed
```

Bearer tokens and API keys are read from env at runtime. They are never
written to logs (`framework/logger.py` redacts `Authorization` and the
configured `API_KEY_HEADER` values before any log output).

`runs/<env>/api_tests.log` may contain request paths and response bodies.
The `runs/` directory is gitignored except for `.gitkeep` files.

